# === C++ Compiled Binaries ===
# USACO compiles .cpp to same-name executable (no extension)
# Ignore all files, then selectively un-ignore sources

# Ignore everything by default
*

# Un-ignore directories (so files inside can be evaluated)
!*/

# Un-ignore C++ source and header files
!*.cpp
!*.h
!*.hpp

# Un-ignore gitkeep
!.gitkeep

# Un-ignore this file
!.gitignore
